CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780016591
OL,3,CShopping with AI leads to more sales
OL,4,Cthan by traditional online searches `
OL,5,CAdobe
OL,7,FShopping with the help of AI is now
OL,8,Fleading to more sales in the UK than
OL,9,Fthose via more traditional online
OL,10,Fsearches, figures suggest.
OL,12,FThis month, shoppers clicking through
OL,13,Fto UK retail sites from AI sources
OL,14,Fwere more likely to complete a
OL,15,Fpurchase than those arriving after
OL,16,Fusing online search engines, computer
OL,17,Fsoftware and analytics firm Adobe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780016591
OL,3,CShopping with AI leads to more sales
OL,4,Cthan by traditional online searches `
OL,5,CAdobe
OL,7,FFigures for May show the UK AI
OL,8,Fshopping conversion rate was up 182%
OL,9,Fyear-on-year and 543% since January
OL,10,Flast year.
OL,12,FThe AI shopping conversion rate
OL,13,Fmeasures the percentage of online
OL,14,Fvisitors who interact with AI-powered
OL,15,Ftools such as conversational chatbots
OL,16,Fand who then go on to buy an item.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780016591
OL,3,CShopping with AI leads to more sales
OL,4,Cthan by traditional online searches `
OL,5,CAdobe
OL,7,FInstead of typing keywords into search
OL,8,Fengines and scrolling through the
OL,9,Fresults, shoppers are asking AI a
OL,10,Fquestion and getting a single answer,
OL,11,Foften with a direct link to buy.
OL,13,FAdobe, which has been tracking AI
OL,14,Freferrals to retail sites since August
OL,15,F2024, saw AI-driven traffic grow 393%
OL,16,Fin the first quarter of this year
OL,17,Fcompared with the same period last
OL,18,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780016591
OL,3,CShopping with AI leads to more sales
OL,4,Cthan by traditional online searches `
OL,5,CAdobe
OL,7,FSome 37% of UK consumers have already
OL,8,Fused an AI assistant for online
OL,9,Fshopping, most commonly for research
OL,10,F(43%) and product recommendations
OL,11,F(40%), separate polling for Adobe has
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FSome 65% of those using AI trusted it
OL,15,Fto provide accurate results, while 70%
OL,16,Fsaid AI assistants were now their
OL,17,Fprimary source of product research.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
