PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780016591
OL,3,CShopping with AI leads to more sales
OL,4,Cthan by traditional online searches `
OL,5,CAdobe
OL,7,FVivek Pandya, director of Adobe
OL,8,FDigital Insights, said: "As shoppers
OL,9,Fhave learned to trust AI tools, they
OL,10,Ffeel more assured about their
OL,11,Fpurchases and return fewer items.
OL,13,F"AI traffic is increasingly consistent
OL,14,Fin converting better than traditional
OL,15,Fchannels and adoption continues to
OL,16,Faccelerate.
