OL,3,CShopping with AI leads to more sales
OL,4,Cthan by traditional online searches `
OL,5,CAdobe
OL,7,F"For retailers, the clear message is
OL,8,Fto make sure your digital properties
OL,9,Fare AI-ready. This isn't a 'nice to
OL,10,Fhave' any more ` it's key to remain
OL,11,Frelevant and to convert more sales
OL,12,Fwithin this new retail landscape."
